🎈 Sorting Visualizer

An interactive and animated sorting visualizer built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

🚀 Features
- Bubble Sort, Selection Sort, Insertion Sort
- Smooth balloon-based animations 🎈
- Pause, Resume, Stop functionality
- Adjustable animation speed
- User input support

🎨 Highlights
- Clean and modern UI
- Animated gradient background
- Visual learning of sorting algorithms

🛠 Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

 📌 Live Demo
 https://preetikotabagi.github.io/sorting-visualizer/


✨ Built with focus on both logic and user experience
